query:
SELECT et.id, et.employeeId, e.name as employeeName, et.targetType, et.targetValue, et.currentValue, et.year, et.month, et.status
FROM employeeTargets et
JOIN employees e ON et.employeeId = e.id
WHERE et.year = 2026 AND et.month = 1
ORDER BY e.name;
